422
00:22:08.661 --> 00:22:10.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Carmen] Entonces,
te tengo una misión.

423
00:22:10.704 --> 00:22:12.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Atraviesa</i>
<i>la cinta de la policía,</i>

424
00:22:12.665 --> 00:22:14.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>entra a la oficina de Ninibé</i>

425
00:22:14.583 --> 00:22:16.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>y busca cualquier pista</i>

426
00:22:16.377 --> 00:22:18.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>de quién puede ser</i>
<i>su discípula, por favor.</i>

427
00:22:37.273 --> 00:22:39.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
