428
00:22:39.108 --> 00:22:41.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Carmen, Carmen,
tenemos serios problemas.

429
00:22:41.819 --> 00:22:43.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
