430
00:22:43.195 --> 00:22:44.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, sí, sí pude entrar,

431
00:22:44.601 --> 00:22:46.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
